name: SR Radio - "You're Listening To..."
description:
"If you like your punk rock high tempo with a melodic edge, this is definitely worth checking out. UK punk rockers SR Radio bursting on to the scene with a sound resembling the West-Coast, California skate-punk scene. All this while still staying true to an all-English sound. This demo is filled with a high energy guitar sound that will hypnotize you with catchy riffs, and choruses you can’t help but want to sing along to after a couple of listens. The highlight of the demo without a doubt has to be ‘doomed if I do’ with its captivating tone that will simply put a smile on your face." 
- 
dirtyskankerpublications.wordpress.com

Tracklist:

1. Party at Andersons
2. Chorus of Indifference
3. Doomed if I do
4. Renegades
5. SRT

Mixed by Daly George, Front man of Drones - www.facebook.com/dronesuk
